      <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout">
       <item row="3" column="0">
        <widget class="QLabel" name="label_2">
         <property name="text">
          <string>DCS-BIOS in this mode uses the official Git repository on GitHub, which allows it to stay constantly up to date. Even the smallest updates and fixes will be immediately available. However, it requires **Git** to be installed on your system. If you know what you’re doing, you can select a specific branch or commit from the repository.

**Note**: The DCS-BIOS developers recommend using DCS-BIOS in this way.</string>
