       <item row="3" column="1">
        <widget class="QLabel" name="label_3">
         <property name="text">
          <string>In this mode, you use DCS-BIOS in a more old-fashioned, traditional way. DCSpy will install the latest available release of DCS-BIOS from the GitHub releases page of the project.

This means you’ll be using a stable, tested official version, but new features and fixes will not be available until the DCS-BIOS developers release a new version.</string>
         </property>
